# Data Mart (Star Schema)

This folder contains the SQL scripts for the **Data Mart layer**, which is designed
using a **star schema**.

The Data Mart is optimized for analytical queries and reporting and is built
on top of the Data Vault core.

## Components

- **Dimension tables (DIM)**  
  Provide descriptive context such as product, region, reseller, and salesperson.

- **Fact tables (FACT)**  
  Store measurable business events such as sales quantities, revenue, and cost.

The Data Mart simplifies access to the data and enables efficient analysis
for BI tools and ad-hoc SQL queries.
